### List all loggers and their current levels
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/loggers

### Get the level of a specific logger
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/loggers/com.danielleitelima

### Set log level to DEBUG at runtime — no restart required
POST http://localhost:8080/actuator/loggers/com.danielleitelima
Content-Type: application/json

{"configuredLevel": "DEBUG"}

### Set log level to TRACE for deeper inspection
POST http://localhost:8080/actuator/loggers/com.danielleitelima
Content-Type: application/json

{"configuredLevel": "TRACE"}

### Reset to the default level configured in application.yaml
POST http://localhost:8080/actuator/loggers/com.danielleitelima
Content-Type: application/json

{"configuredLevel": null}
